{"word":"G4103 - πιστός - pistós - pis-tos' - Believe","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πιστός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>pistós"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>pis-tos'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Believe"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"உண்மையான, உண்மையுள்ள, நிச்சயமான, விசுவாசமுள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. trusty, faithful"},{"paragraph":"2. easily persuaded; believing, confiding, trusting"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G3982 - πείθω - peíthō - pi'-tho/3982\">G3982</a>; objectively <i>trustworthy</i>; subjectively <i>trustful:</i> - believe (-ing, -r), faithful (-ly), sure, true."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3640 - ὀλιγόπιστος - oligópistos - ol-ig-op'-is-tos/3640\">G3640</a>, <a href=\"#/G4100 - πιστεύω - pisteúō - pist-yoo'-o/4100\">G4100</a>, <a href=\"#/G4102 - πίστις - pístis - pis'-tis/4102\">G4102</a>, <a href=\"#/G4103 - πιστός - pistós - pis-tos'/4103\">G4103</a>, <a href=\"#/G4104 - πιστόω - pistóō - pis-to'-o/4104\">G4104</a>, <a href=\"#/G569 - ἀπιστέω - apistéō - ap-is-teh'-o/569\">G569</a>, <a href=\"#/G570 - ἀπιστία - apistía - ap-is-tee'-ah/570\">G570</a>, <a href=\"#/G571 - ἄπιστος - ápistos - ap'-is-tos/571\">G571</a>"}]}